The primary endpoint for this schema is:

```http
GET /v1/transactions/{businessTransactionId}
```

It is also returned by:

```http
POST /v1/transactions
```

when a new Business Transaction is successfully created (or an existing one is returned due to idempotency).

### Response Mapping

| Endpoint                                       | Method | Response Schema                                      |
| ---------------------------------------------- | ------ | ---------------------------------------------------- |
| `POST /v1/transactions`                        | POST   | `schemas/responses/transaction-response.schema.json` |
| `GET /v1/transactions/{businessTransactionId}` | GET    | `schemas/responses/transaction-response.schema.json` |

### Purpose

This response represents the current state of the Business Transaction, including:

* Business Transaction identifier
* Metadata
* Policy
* Signals
* Decision
* Current lifecycle status
* Related resource links

Subsequent resources have their own dedicated response schemas:

| Endpoint                                                   | Response Schema                               |
| ---------------------------------------------------------- | --------------------------------------------- |
| `POST /v1/transactions/{businessTransactionId}/executions` | `execution-response.schema.json`              |
| `GET /v1/transactions/{businessTransactionId}/executions`  | `execution-response.schema.json` (collection) |
| `POST /v1/transactions/{businessTransactionId}/override`   | `override-response.schema.json`               |
| `POST /v1/transactions/{businessTransactionId}/verify`     | `verification-response.schema.json`           |
| `GET /v1/transactions/{businessTransactionId}/receipt`     | `receipt-response.schema.json`                |
| `GET /v1/transactions/{businessTransactionId}/trust-chain` | `trust-chain-response.schema.json`            |

This keeps each API resource aligned with its own response contract while using the Business Transaction response as the canonical representation of the primary resource.


{
  "$schema": "https://json-schema.org/draft/2020-12/schema",
  "$id": "https://schemas.parmana.ai/responses/transaction-response.schema.json",
  "title": "Transaction Response",
  "description": "Response returned for a Business Transaction.",
  "type": "object",
  "additionalProperties": false,
  "required": [
    "data"
  ],
  "properties": {
    "data": {
      "type": "object",
      "additionalProperties": false,
      "required": [
        "businessTransactionId",
        "metadata",
        "policy",
        "signals",
        "decision",
        "status",
        "createdAt"
      ],
      "properties": {
        "businessTransactionId": {
          "type": "string",
          "description": "Unique Business Transaction identifier."
        },
        "metadata": {
          "$ref": "../common/metadata.schema.json"
        },
        "policy": {
          "$ref": "../common/policy.schema.json"
        },
        "signals": {
          "type": "object",
          "description": "Business signals evaluated by the resolved policy.",
          "additionalProperties": true
        },
        "decision": {
          "$ref": "../common/decision.schema.json"
        },
        "status": {
          "type": "string",
          "description": "Current Business Transaction lifecycle state.",
          "enum": [
            "RECEIVED",
            "EXECUTING",
            "COMPLETED",
            "FAILED"
          ]
        },
        "createdAt": {
          "type": "string",
          "format": "date-time",
          "description": "UTC timestamp when the Business Transaction was created."
        },
        "links": {
          "type": "object",
          "description": "Related API resources.",
          "additionalProperties": false,
          "properties": {
            "self": {
              "type": "string",
              "format": "uri"
            },
            "executions": {
              "type": "string",
              "format": "uri"
            },
            "override": {
              "type": "string",
              "format": "uri"
            },
            "receipt": {
              "type": "string",
              "format": "uri"
            },
            "verifications": {
              "type": "string",
              "format": "uri"
            },
            "trustChain": {
              "type": "string",
              "format": "uri"
            }
          }
        }
      }
    }
  },
  "examples": [
    {
      "data": {
        "businessTransactionId": "PAY-1001",
        "metadata": {
          "businessTransactionId": "PAY-1001"
        },
        "policy": {
          "name": "payment-approval",
          "version": "2.1.0",
          "schemaVersion": "1.0"
        },
        "signals": {
          "amount": 5000,
          "currency": "USD"
        },
        "decision": {
          "outcome": "APPROVED",
          "evaluatedAt": "2026-06-26T10:15:43Z"
        },
        "status": "RECEIVED",
        "createdAt": "2026-06-26T10:15:40Z",
        "links": {
          "self": "/v1/transactions/PAY-1001",
          "executions": "/v1/transactions/PAY-1001/executions",
          "override": "/v1/transactions/PAY-1001/override",
          "receipt": "/v1/transactions/PAY-1001/receipt",
          "verifications": "/v1/transactions/PAY-1001/verifications",
          "trustChain": "/v1/transactions/PAY-1001/trust-chain"
        }
      }
    }
  ]
}